          "reviewBody": "I studied here for 2years 8std & 9std... very lovely & adventure memories 2006 - 2008 anyone from this batch like or reply. my fndz name i remembered sriram, pushparaj, ranjith, sridhar, fareen Fatima, rabina, malavika etc others name i can't remember sry l. Totally 12 is our class strength. Teachers i miss tamil teacher, English teacher, botany teacher ( principal) , history teacher, pet teacher and Physics teacher...i remember all their face , not the name... Very humble people.... Unlikely i can't continue my studies their ..",
