            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "A proud alumni student of MPA!\n\nI came from Vidya Mandir,  thought I might face challenges but from day one it was a great experience.  I was here for two years from 2017 to 2019 for my plus one and plus two. Served as a prefect here that leveled up my confidence, changed by perspectives. A great thanks to our late principal Amudha ma'aIm. Janani ma'am and all the teachers here take extra care and give personal attention to each and every student in their academics and extracurricular activities. They actually made me study and score well.XD!\nZero motivation in studies to an Outstanding student of the year 2017!",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
