          "reviewBody": "I have no words to describe this school because If I say something good also it will be less. But I just want to say that if parents are searching for the one of the best school in chennai this school will be a perfect for the good teacher's, knowledge, facilities of learning  & management, good caring and specially a principal mam of this school Mrs Janani Laxmi. She tooked a responsibility of the whole school  after our late principal mam Mrs Amudha Anand. Iam not saying this because I'm a student in this institute actually I had been experienced a lot because I had  study this school from LKG and next year I am going to complete my higher studies.",
